But when a female is educated, she does not comply blindly and learns to think and care for herself too in the same way. Secondly, when female gets - - - education, she secures economic sustenance for herself. In this way she does not depend on any one economically and can make impartial, out of free will decision for the future. This protects her from blindly following someone just because they materially provide for them According to UNFD (United Nations Population Fund) there is only 28% female labour force which means the other 72% women are economi- cally dependent on their male guardian. Hence, when the female is educated, she comes out of this vicious cycle of dependence and makes decisions for herself just as she likes.
